des:
MusicXChange radio supports positive change through the power of music. We are composed of a diverse group of volunteer musicians, artists, producers and others, united by a common passion for record making and music production, and by a strong desire to address inequalities in the world.

MUSICXCHANGE is an international nonprofit organization, recognized as a 501(c)(3) tax exempt public charity under U.S. law.
